GLT - new on market

This home was rebuilt on a local sheep farm that dates back to the 1820s. With the history of the property you get the best of both worlds - the charm and style of an older American home and the amenities and finishes of a modern luxurious home. Garland Road hasn't had a home on the market in over 50 years, so this is a rare opportunity to relocate to such a prime location.

cur_data.desc: 2 levels of spacious living in the heart of Newtonville (1,854 sf). Kitchen just updated with granite counters/stainless appliances. Short walk to schools, train, Shaws, Whole Foods, Trader Joe's. Wide open living areas have large picture windows with south & east views of the village. Large BRs have big closets. Master has walk-in & direct access to full bath. 3rd BR also makes perfect office with corner windows. Sliding doors access a covered balcony in the trees.

This gorgeous, newly reconstructed luxury apartment with modern floor plan features designer furniture, furnishings, accessories, high ceilings and flush mount halogen lighting throughout the entire apartment. An exquisite kitchen with a complete complement of high quality kitchen accessories, granite countertops and island counter. In addition, a 42 inch Plasma TV, Sony Playstation 3, CD and DVD player and stereo in the main living area, an Italian design walk-in closet in the master bedroom, large Jacuzzi tub in the master bath and designer furniture throughout. Dimmer controlled lighting in the main living area. The two extra bedrooms feature American style closets with sliding doors. The smaller bedroom also doubles as an office. TV channels include CNN, BBC and many other English language channels. The common areas of the building are clean, well kept and the building has a working elevator. The apartment sleeps 6 adults comfortably.

Townhouse right in the heart of Conshohocken! Within walking distance are all the neighborhood shops you'll need. 2 parking spaces included - 1 is covered. Large kitchen with bar area eating, brand new appliances, granite counters. Floors are also new. Large bedrooms for the area. All heating and A/C were updated in last 5 years.

WOW! This nice 3 bedroom 1.5 bath Cape home sits on a level 10,156 square foot lot! Very desirable street and location! Beautiful hardwood floors throughout! 1st floor has front to back living room with fireplace, dining room, office/playroom, kitchen and half bath. 2nd floor has a big master with great closets, two more good size bedrooms, and a full bath. Partially finished basement with laundry. Awesome yard! One car attached garage. Needs some updating but well worth it. Must see!

Sunny & spacious, this condominium has it all; quiet street close to West Newton Ctr, commuter rail & Mass Pike; 1 gar. space & 1 driveway space; oak floors, natural woodwork; gut remodel with soundproofing, new windows, walls & updated kitchen w/ oak cabinets and silestone countertops; newer Knight Lochinvar energy efficient 3 zone heat; solid back porch overlooking a huge yard shaded by a mature oak tree. Sun room w/ windows on 3 sides off the living room. 1st Open House June 10 1-2:30.
